Von Frau Komorn durch einen Boten drei Bände Neumann; mittlere Sammlung;
              Mittlere Sammlung (Majjhima Nikaya) (Collection of Middle-length Discourses): part of the Suttapitaka, a collection of the Buddha's dialogues and didactical lectures. The only complete German translation of the Pali original was done by Carl Eugen Neumann between 1896 and 1902.
